-- coherence.cell: Experiment 2 вЂ” Cross-reference coherence test
-- 3 citizens who KNOW each other. Analyst checks if their stories are consistent.
-- Tests: soft cell dispatch, cross-referencing, analyst coherence detection
-- Run: rt load && rt sling в†’ dispatch citizens в†’ rt collect в†’ rt sling в†’ dispatch analyst в†’ rt collect

вЉў city
  yield description в‰Ў "Millhaven is a small coastal town. Harbor district with fishing boats. Main street with shops and a library. Residential hill with Victorian houses. Old lighthouse on the point. Overcast Tuesday in March."
  yield day в‰Ў "Tuesday, March 4"
  yield shared-event в‰Ў "A fishing boat ran aground on the rocks near the lighthouse at dawn. The coast guard arrived by 8 AM. Half the town came to watch."

вЉў witness-anna
  given cityв†’description
  given cityв†’day
  given cityв†’shared-event
  yield name в‰Ў "Anna Kowalski"
  yield age в‰Ў 34
  yield occupation в‰Ў "harbor patrol officer"
  yield morning
  yield afternoon
  yield evening
  yield account-of-event
  в€ґ You are В«nameВ», age В«ageВ», the В«occupationВ» of Millhaven.
    Town: В«descriptionВ». Today is В«dayВ».

    IMPORTANT EVENT TODAY: В«shared-eventВ»
    You were ON DUTY when this happened. You were one of the first responders.

    Live your day. Describe morning, afternoon, evening.
    Also give your detailed account of the boat grounding вЂ” what you saw,
    who you talked to, what happened. Be specific about times and people.
  вЉЁ morning is a string
  вЉЁ account-of-event is a string

вЉў witness-carlos
  given cityв†’description
  given cityв†’day
  given cityв†’shared-event
  yield name в‰Ў "Carlos Reyes"
  yield age в‰Ў 52
  yield occupation в‰Ў "lighthouse keeper"
  yield morning
  yield afternoon
  yield evening
  yield account-of-event
  в€ґ You are В«nameВ», age В«ageВ», the В«occupationВ» of Millhaven.
    Town: В«descriptionВ». Today is В«dayВ».

    IMPORTANT EVENT TODAY: В«shared-eventВ»
    You were AT THE LIGHTHOUSE when this happened. You saw it from above.

    Live your day. Describe morning, afternoon, evening.
    Also give your detailed account of the boat grounding вЂ” what you saw
    from the lighthouse, who arrived, what happened. Be specific.
  вЉЁ morning is a string
  вЉЁ account-of-event is a string

вЉў witness-elena
  given cityв†’description
  given cityв†’day
  given cityв†’shared-event
  yield name в‰Ў "Elena Marsh"
  yield age в‰Ў 67
  yield occupation в‰Ў "retired teacher who walks the shore every morning"
  yield morning
  yield afternoon
  yield evening
  yield account-of-event
  в€ґ You are В«nameВ», age В«ageВ», a В«occupationВ» in Millhaven.
    Town: В«descriptionВ». Today is В«dayВ».

    IMPORTANT EVENT TODAY: В«shared-eventВ»
    You were ON YOUR MORNING WALK on the shore when this happened.
    You saw it unfold from the beach.

    Live your day. Describe morning, afternoon, evening.
    Also give your detailed account of the boat grounding вЂ” what you saw
    from the shore, who you talked to afterward. Be specific.
  вЉЁ morning is a string
  вЉЁ account-of-event is a string

вЉў coherence-analyst
  given witness-annaв†’name
  given witness-annaв†’occupation
  given witness-annaв†’account-of-event
  given witness-carlosв†’name
  given witness-carlosв†’occupation
  given witness-carlosв†’account-of-event
  given witness-elenaв†’name
  given witness-elenaв†’occupation
  given witness-elenaв†’account-of-event
  yield timeline-reconstruction
  yield contradictions
  yield corroborations
  yield reliability-ranking
  yield coherence-score
  в€ґ You are a forensic analyst comparing three witness accounts of the same event:
    a fishing boat running aground near the Millhaven lighthouse at dawn.

    === В«witness-annaв†’nameВ» (В«witness-annaв†’occupationВ») ===
    В«witness-annaв†’account-of-eventВ»

    === В«witness-carlosв†’nameВ» (В«witness-carlosв†’occupationВ») ===
    В«witness-carlosв†’account-of-eventВ»

    === В«witness-elenaв†’nameВ» (В«witness-elenaв†’occupationВ») ===
    В«witness-elenaв†’account-of-eventВ»

    Analyze:
    1. timeline-reconstruction: Reconstruct a single timeline from all three accounts.
    2. contradictions: List any contradictions between accounts (times, people, details).
    3. corroborations: List details that multiple witnesses agree on.
    4. reliability-ranking: Rank the three witnesses by reliability, with reasoning.
    5. coherence-score: Rate 1-10 how coherent these three accounts are together.
       10 = perfectly consistent, 1 = wildly contradictory.
  вЉЁ timeline-reconstruction is a string
  вЉЁ contradictions is a string
  вЉЁ corroborations is a string
  вЉЁ coherence-score is a string
